# PennyLLM — Provider API Keys
# Copy to .env and fill in keys you have
#
# Target providers (7): Cerebras, Google, Groq, GitHub Models,
# SambaNova, NVIDIA NIM, Mistral
#
# Dropped providers: HuggingFace ($0.10/mo too small), Cohere (1K calls/mo),
# Cloudflare (10K neurons/day too small), Qwen/DashScope (region-locked),
# OpenRouter (per-account limits, all models available directly elsewhere),
# Together AI (one-time credit only), DeepSeek (one-time trial),
# Fireworks (one-time credit only)

# --- Tier 1: Best perpetual free tiers ---

# Cerebras — 1M tokens/day, 30 RPM, fastest inference (2,500 tok/s)
# https://cloud.cerebras.ai
CEREBRAS_API_KEY=

# Google AI Studio (Gemini) — 10-15 RPM, 100-1000 RPD, multi-project keys
# Limits are per-project — create up to 10 projects for 10 independent quota pools
# https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=
# Optional: additional project keys for key rotation
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY_2=
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY_3=

# Groq — 30-60 RPM, 1K-14.4K RPD per model, ultra-fast LPU inference
# https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=

# GitHub Models — ONLY free access to o3, o4-mini, GPT-4o
# 50 RPD high-tier, 150 RPD low-tier. Just needs a GitHub account.
# https://github.com/marketplace/models
GITHUB_MODELS_API_KEY=

# --- Tier 2: Persistent free + unique value ---

# SambaNova — ONLY free access to full DeepSeek-R1 671B
# Free tier: 20 RPD (tiny). Developer tier (link card, $0 balance): 12,000 RPD
# https://cloud.sambanova.ai
SAMBANOVA_API_KEY=

# NVIDIA NIM — Broadest model catalog (DeepSeek R1, Kimi K2.5 ~1T, etc.)
# 1,000 credits on signup (one-time), 40 RPM
# https://build.nvidia.com
NVIDIA_API_KEY=

# Mistral — Own frontier models (Mistral Large 3), 1 RPS, 1B tokens/month
# Phone verification required
# https://console.mistral.ai/api-keys
MISTRAL_API_KEY=
